description:
Adecco is the world’s leading HR service provider with an international background, specializing in temporary and permanent employment, career and talent development, outsourcing and consulting services. For our internal team in Slovenia, we are looking for a candidate to join us as a:
Payroll Intern
(Serbia, remote-based role)
Key responsibilities:
Entering employee sick leave records into the system;
Updating and maintaining employee attendance records;
Processing and recording HR changes (e.g., new hires, terminations, status changes);
Performing other administrative tasks related to payroll preparation.
Candidate profile:
You are a fresh graduate or in your final year of studies;
You are comfortable working with numbers, have strong numerical skills, and pay close attention to detail;
You have a proactive attitude and are not afraid to dive into assigned tasks;
You have a good command of Microsoft Office and the English language;
Knowledge of the Slovenian language is considered an advantage.
